{
  "stem": "1160.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody's coming back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there is such a silence, such a silence, I remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything was so silent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And-- and the women, the-- the wives and the daughters-- my mother was there-- and they were looking out from the door.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The door had a glass door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was always-- I don't know, always outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They wanted me to come into the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I knew they wanted me to come in, but I didn't listen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was just there in the yard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this was a long walkway toward-- to the-- from the fence, from which-- from the sidewalk or the street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There's the sidewalk, and there was the door to the yard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it's a long walk up to the Safar house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's how it seemed to me at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "As a small child, everything was big and large.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was a-- a [NON-ENGLISH] came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "To me he looked very tall, dressed in boots, uniform, very neat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he had a-- a sword in his hand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I looked towards the door and they were-- my family said to come, come, and I was very curious what this man is going to do.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But somehow, I had a little bit of fear already, because I knew that something is not right here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this [NON-ENGLISH]-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I think his name was Churnik-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he took this sword and he started to dig.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Slowly he was walking, and he was digging, like this, into the earth, on the sidewalk up to the-- up to the house.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
